desc.html: English:  Title: Kunst- u. Figurinenausstellung Abstract: Poster shows a cherub pulling a cart with theatrical (drama and comedy) masks. Poster announces an art exhibit to benefit the Red Cross of Niederösterreich. Details of the exhibition are given. Physical description: 1 print (poster) : lithograph, color ; 60 x 48 cm. Notes: Forms part of: Rehse-Archiv für Zeitgeschichte und Publizistik.; V. Th. Slama.; Title from item.
